OL,6,FA Bollywood inspired singer says she
OL,7,Fwants to encourage a new generation -
OL,8,Fbecause "she did not see artists like
OL,9,Fher growing up".
OL,11,Fwas born in Delhi but moved to Bolton,
OL,12,Fin the North West of England, when she
OL,13,Fwas one years old. Her Indian heritage
OL,14,Fis a big influence in her music.
OL,16,FThe 25-year-old loves Bollywood movies
OL,17,Fbecause they are "loud and bold" and
OL,18,Fthey have inspired both her sound and
OL,19,Fperformances.
