OL,6,FThe artist believes she is filling a
OL,7,Fgap in the market and writes and
OL,8,Fproduces her music on her own label,
OL,9,FRIYAYASH working with her brother Yash
OL,10,Fon her music videos.
OL,12,F"Growing up, I didn't see anybody like
OL,13,Fme in the industry or the media," said
OL,14,FRiya.
OL,16,F"I would love for a young girl to say
OL,17,F'Oh I'd like to do that', because she
OL,18,Fsees that I'm following my dreams and
OL,19,FI'm doing it."
