OL,6,FHer biggest gig so far was performing
OL,7,Fon the BBC Introducing stage at the
OL,8,FHundred in Headingley in 2023.
OL,10,F"It was unreal, I was like, 'this is
OL,11,Fwhat Beyonce feels like' once you have
OL,12,Fperformed to 30,000 people and I won't
OL,13,Fstop until I'm selling out my own
OL,14,Fstadium", said Riya.
OL,16,FThis was also followed by shows at
OL,17,FMacron Stadium, Factory International,
OL,18,Fthe Tate Museum and O2 Academy London.
